           <div class="text" style="left: 10px;">
            <h2>
             <a href="https://greatergood.berkeley.edu/article/item/what_is_the_true_cost_of_polarization_in_america">
              The Price of Polarization
             </a>
            </h2>
            <p>
             If Americans don’t learn to build bridges with each other, we may see more government shutdowns, lying, segregation—and even violence.
            </p>
